{"tid":411703,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]分享一啲已完結嘅打鬥漫畫佳作","createTime":"2017-09-24T05:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T06:09:54.000Z","uid":60288,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5914b1231d45f2cfb34379f2324bbcb83371ddf","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"見動漫台成日都係火影，<br />\n想講下其他高質得嚟比較少人討論嘅中長篇打鬥漫畫，<br />\n講已完結因為佢地故事完整，唔會之後暴走/拖戲，<br />\n下面唔少都係名作，可能睇得漫畫多嘅都睇過，志在拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鋼煉神作唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n1. Hellsing　全10冊<br />\n吸血鬼打鬥、Boss型主角。畫風、人物動作同對白都展現出強烈嘅風格。故事完整，節奏好，冇多餘枝節。推薦OVA動畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/125322_0ad74d2d3235cdf36e52964f11241e0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F125322_0ad74d2d3235cdf36e52964f11241e0c.png&h=38707f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 打鬼　全13冊<br />\n靈異戰鬥漫畫，打鬥畫面出色，極爽快、震撼。故事好多殘忍情節，營造出恐怖感，但因為主角方好強大好有魄力，所以唔會令人覺得壓抑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/125552_2c7fa33c63ee24641d2aba61b3e3b596.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F125552_2c7fa33c63ee24641d2aba61b3e3b596.png&h=4a69ad24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 大劍　全27冊<br />\n妖魔打鬥漫畫，世界觀幾特別。打嘅幾乎全部都係女，用嘅武器一樣都係劍，但技能唔同，每個角色都有特色。前半情節比較灰暗、營造出絕望、壓迫感，但後面就冇咗咁嘅感覺，偏向少年漫，但BOSS戰我覺得好正。有動畫但唔好睇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/125756_c0bd84341c99a0873af3f387cf46d758.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F125756_c0bd84341c99a0873af3f387cf46d758.png&h=f4339776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. ALIVE 最終進化少年　全21冊<br />\n超能力打鬥漫畫，角色個性刻畫得唔錯，好多角色包括反派都有自己過去，有陰暗面。第一部我覺得比較精彩刺激，第二部又係變得比較似普通少年漫。整體上幾感人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/125401_08821d3e4ed2d0c3b5b9516e9aa6b39f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F125401_08821d3e4ed2d0c3b5b9516e9aa6b39f.png&h=9314269d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d821c2d90f4814448342c5bfaf3530fb095e8027","tid":411703,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:07:35.000Z","msg":"軍雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80e9f77f7311e89dfc1ca4c29d1825cc9e961ce","tid":411703,"uid":5590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"大劍正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcbe2604ee27fea4516a61139df9c973b04e638","tid":411703,"uid":134825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314662d3a675eee6e3e2f4330deaa68bbd5599f3","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見動漫台成日都係火影，<br />\n想講下其他高質得嚟比較少人討論嘅中長篇打鬥漫畫，<br />\n講已完結因為佢地故事完整，唔會之後暴走/拖戲，<br />\n下面唔少都係名作，可能睇得漫畫多嘅都睇過，志在拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鋼<span style=\"color: red;\">鍊</span>神作唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e8f0e561e1fe537c04a4d0644358908d06226","tid":411703,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>軍雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好講依套垃圾了..."},{"pid":"2d2bdfcd51d0cf5b64ad42e27f9e356fe85632a7","tid":411703,"uid":20362,