if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說成嶋亮打東馬先<br />\n定係學中國功夫先<br />\n<br />\nBTW捍衛聖域唔錯</blockquote><br />\n學功夫先, 不過中國篇好似變咗黑歷史, 學埋啲嘢後面冇再出現過</blockquote><br />\nyes   有中國篇就接唔到後面D劇情"},{"pid":"e09c933f5b6a1b6556e77cbad2e79b0b3804d9cd","tid":411703,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"天上天下"},{"pid":"c8086920ed7938bcaeeecba1ae217c10b26a73fc","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>螺旋卷勾生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身以為係賣囡囡賣萌<br />\n之後睇落又唔錯 啲顏藝幾有特色幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5103fccc99f615a441cfb7016feffaf7e43d55fc","tid":411703,"uid":96032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"戰國妖狐"},{"pid":"c964fba64ff3b96cfb4cb82add14dc86f14dc164","tid":411703,"uid":15703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:15:47.000Z","msg":"兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5377befdcfd34da791f94749c15876016c5e0d29","tid":411703,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜出版社執"},{"pid":"bc9c6ad2dae2836814cedb1d52270694cd9360d4","tid":411703,"uid":124868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"alive點解唔揀奈美架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg