"2017-09-24T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推埋新暗行御史，burning blood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新暗行御史我覺得有啲似烙印勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面唔錯，幾好睇，後期開始亂，而個尾真係見過最爛之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嘥咗<br />\n不過畫方面好出色，睇完哩套覺得其他韓漫(webtoon嗰堆)都睇唔落去"},{"pid":"21828e671e4643f056c9113e7bb0afc5e5e785c4","tid":411703,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"冇劍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7ba23f7c3d8db559bc70c95597e12778bbc8ce","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇劍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我比較鐘意成套漫畫一個主線一個故事，多過有好多單元／幾篇嘅故事<br />\n劍心我睇完志志雄篇就冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdec973915d9547d8b7a4ba3d088924a498e68c","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>alive話時話<br />\n男主能力係嘜野&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱＋再生⇄死滅<br />\n造成嘅傷回復唔到<br />\n用手掂到先有用"},{"pid":"4a7c7b0921ccc7774d366d559cf536634bb5a51a","tid":411703,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"刃牙身1部"},{"pid":"89eeea1210f878311f289c1f8ce5748279291f50","tid":411703,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"大劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8a1b23ffaa67fea7b14bb21aefba861a4907a0","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"少年漫嚟講，<br />\n救世之繭都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/170354_5c8381a80a8d9dad28a1d453c54ae84c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F170354_5c8381a80a8d9dad28a1d453c54ae84c.png&h=22f7c261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情完整、人物情感刻劃得唔錯，啲面部表情／分鏡好出色，營造到氣氛，帶動情緒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/170918_fad7c091bc7caad4bfec7959c308d1a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F170918_fad7c091bc7caad4bfec7959c308d1a4.png&h=7697b4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋結尾都好感人"},{"pid":"3a3ce73f5f8d6f6346199c3962557b80e8674d15","tid":411703,"uid":84010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d"},{"pid":"b1b3c0deec4d2a43a8ca62c0493fd2c103b61601","tid":411703,"uid":135019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浪客劍心算唔算</blockquote><br />\n俾你講左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死囚樂園"},{"pid":"e9e740640b5856cdcf67b16e7209babe4258ad2c","tid":411703,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d</blockquote><br />\n個個師傳都各有特色，重睇左呢套野好多次<br />\n雖然個結局差唔多係：想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa26e39b67aefdd7507850149d1770d158c9582","tid":411703,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d</blockquote><br />\n個個師傳都各有特色，重睇左呢套野好多次<br />\n雖然個結局差唔多係：想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlast接受唔到弟子係配角，師傅變主線"},{"pid":"61d7b752647ac04c3776f90dd554eb580a7f6fc1","tid":411703,"uid":117909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"鬼眼狂刀點睇？<br />\n套野雖然啲角色能力好唔平衡 有啲七龍珠式打怪feel 不過啲技同角色真係好型 主線劇情又幾吸引"},{"pid":"80da47e897c5b7a6e7be90005b6a83d5fb504c83","tid":411703,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼眼狂刀點睇？<br />\n套野雖然啲角色能力好唔平衡 有啲七龍珠式打怪feel 不過啲技同角色真係好型 主線劇情又幾吸引</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼眼，烈火，閃靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dae0cf8c8d71cb11cda0477fa7015aea5c37180","tid":411703,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少年漫嚟講，<br />\n救世之繭都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/170354_5c8381a80a8d9dad28a1d453c54ae84c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F170354_5c8381a80a8d9dad28a1d453c54ae84c.png&h=22f7c261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情完整、人物情感刻劃得唔錯，啲面部表情／分鏡好出色，營造到氣氛，帶動情緒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/170918_fad7c091bc7caad4bfec7959c308d1a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F170918_fad7c091bc7caad4bfec7959c308d1a4.png&h=7697b4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋結尾都好感人</blockquote><br />\n呢套個尾算係咁<br />\n有個好結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16089a20e97d62cdeace1241b6e47178e0d3c99c","tid":411703,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d</blockquote><br />\n個個師傳都各有特色，重睇左呢套野好多次<br />\n雖然個結局差唔多係：想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlast接受唔到弟子係配角，師傅變主線</blockquote><br />\n又唔係話配角既，只係兩邊一齊打咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4fad01f7ca12bda99950f5775423e3f6371cc5","tid":411703,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>alive好似個作者就死都作埋先死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未完就死咗 聽講係作埋個結尾先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知作畫有冇跟住畫<br />\n作畫之後自己嗰套野良神我麻麻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身可以動畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係間公司破左產<br />\n原著知道左消息後冇幾耐就過左世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c193febaffcf851eea0b2f8152e82153a0ae22","tid":411703,"uid":84010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兼