戲份越嚟越少</blockquote><br />\n到最後都無講哂無敵超人108招絕招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a597e8f9134f502ccab0d0bd5498f0a09b973d","tid":411703,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兼一算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d</blockquote><br />\n個個師傳都各有特色，重睇左呢套野好多次<br />\n雖然個結局差唔多係：想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlast接受唔到弟子係配角，師傅變主線</blockquote><br />\n又唔係話配角既，只係兩邊一齊打咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇過漫畫好多次+1，動畫睇唔落去，接受唔到把聲<br />\n好鐘意班師傅，徒弟無感<br />\n最鐘意阿帕差vs阿迦德既巔峰之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得出打完葉翔之後慢慢以師傅為重心<br />\n加上又出咗個55周年企劃被逼摺<br />\n收番師傅條主嫌咪搞到徒弟既戲份越嚟越少</blockquote><br />\n到最後都無講哂無敵超人108招絕招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n達人之間既對決其實仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f114e6bfbcdc64dacebc6d75f168575f14e240d1","tid":411703,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n本來幾鐘意時雨<br />\n但睇最尾果幾集<br />\n被腰斬都勁賣肉浪費篇幅<br />\n睇到好火<br />\n寧願佢交代劇情詳細d</blockquote><br />\n個個師傳都各有特色，重睇左呢套野好多次<br />\n雖然個結局差唔多係：想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlast接受唔到弟子係配角，師傅變主線</blockquote><br />\n又唔係話配角既，只係兩邊一齊打咁解<img src