<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n達人之間既對決其實仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇住兼一進步其實都幾正，起碼真係唔算主角威能，係遊樂場同奧丁聯手個到又係好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兼一成日鎖血，中勁多招都未輸，睇得多覺得煩<br />\n本來唔多鐘意拳聖，遊樂場果part拳聖既描寫，反而對佢幾有好感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但套野叫最強弟子，我睇緊係睇廢物弟子點變勁啦，久唔久加插下師傅隻揪就ok啫，last師傅變主線真係唔掂真係係為睇時雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:有睇時雨h漫打飛機</blockquote><br />\n對兼一漫畫好有情意結，睇唔落角色既h漫<br />\n單論樣既話，最鐘意美雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f906ec19da9eb2abba1fd73fa182600e31e60eff","tid":411703,"uid":115347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"斬 赤紅之瞳本身我都覺得幾正<br />\n後來愈黎愈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動畫更加唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ec1440c6d2fdd610e3e97c04af11b53134e942","tid":411703,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內衣教父</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你認真?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0aade0816f1db62014fb3e6be3bbe472d280c6","tid":411703,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"正皮比hellsing<br />\n<br />\n女警用 雙大炮打德軍熱氣球好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf53891be5ac4114d6525f9af92385c58e0b5229","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Rave</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖石同妖尾唔知點解我覺得好低齡向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完唔會有咩深刻嘅印象"},{"pid":"ba6bbc4dc38088a9de3d83ddcf34f55e0ce79c06","tid":411703,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T00:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Rave</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖石同妖尾唔知點解我覺得好低齡向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完唔會有咩深刻嘅印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖石好耐之前睇冇印象<br />\n妖尾我諗問題係在於實在太多篇章，而好多段都唔重要又唔深刻，太多故事令人睇得好攰<br />\n我諗冇人可以完整講得出佢個時間線係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有啲人話佢似one piece,  但係我覺得佢故事同人物都淺薄好多，作者功力問題，除咗設定之外無乜可取之處"},{"pid":"0561a270b4dda9b1f6cc11700c1db1a16b9b677b","tid":411703,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>內衣教父</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你認真?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有啲位幾好睇<br />\n雖然中後期大部分都悶"},{"pid":"5a8bc4d061d78c5df22bda05bafc9a883a99dd41","tid":411703,"uid":140454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Rave</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖石同妖尾唔知點解我覺得好低齡向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完唔會有咩深刻嘅印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖石好耐之前睇冇印象<br />\n妖尾我諗問題係在於實在太多篇章，而好多段都唔重要又唔深刻，太多故事令人睇得好攰<br />\n我諗冇人可以完整講得出佢個時間線係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有啲人話佢似one piece,  但係我覺得佢故事同人物都淺薄好多，作者功力問題，除咗設定之外無乜可取之處</blockquote><br />\n真島轉行畫h漫算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc149273302242758c5c5a5db93e45315935af6","tid":411703,"uid":98186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"最強不良傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193bfccbf3ab88e87363e50ce9371b9630c286b0","tid":411703,"uid":60935,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ra